# NOTE: a _redirects rule can NEVER hide a file that exists. Cloudflare Pages serves
# static assets BEFORE consulting this file, so a "/docs/* -> 404" rule silently does
# nothing and the file is served anyway (verified in production, 2026-07-17).
# The publish root IS the repo root: anything committed here is public. Internal docs
# therefore live outside the repo (../website-internal-docs/), not behind a rule.
# Sales OS is its own app under /sales/ - serve it directly, never via the SPA fallback
/sales/*    /sales/:splat    200
# E7: canonicalize duplicate topic URLs to their richer dedicated landing pages
/industry/environmental-remediation    /environmental-remediation-solutions    301
/industry/distributors    /distributors-resellers-industries    301
# Marketing site hash-router SPA fallback
/*    /index.html    200
